manufacturer officials have known about the dangerous games for 
some time said michael jordanreilly spokesman for the hartford 
connbased company 
this is one of our major concerns he said 
at the university of massachusetts at amherst 18yearold joel 
mangion of newton was found dead at the bottom of an elevator shaft 
