she said us inspectors at votkinsk nearly 700 miles east of 
moscow have declared the refusal an ambiguity which she 
called the most serious action our inspectors can take under 
the onsite inspection provisions of the 1987 intermediaterange 
nuclear forces treaty which bans missiles with ranges of 300 to 
3400 miles 
