his fathers connections he was appointed mayor of maceio the 
capital of alagoas under a rightwing military regime that seized 
power in 1964 three years later he was elected to congress on the 
ticket of the regimes official social democratic party 
collor de mello was elected governor of alagoas in 1986 last 
year he formed his own national reconstruction party and announced 
his bid for the presidency 
