at the start of the congressional session sen daniel patrick 
moynihan dny proposed a cut in social security taxes that 
would give wave earners an electionyear break while drawing down 
the trust fund reserves that mask the true size of the federal 
deficit 
if we cant get behind an issue like this im not sure who 
needs the democratic party moynihan said as his proposal faded 
for lack of party support that one clearly worried the white 
