scott paper co allegedly was cheated out 
of up to 1 million by two michigan businessmen and three companies 
that bribed a scott engineer and put his wife on the payroll for 
arranging purchases of needless supplies at inflated prices a 
federal prosecutor said thursday 
william m engelman 52 and gerald m chernow 49 both of 
