european trip told a news conference thursday there was no change 
in the central banks fundamental stance of monitoring the effects 
of its last rate rise put into effect last december 
there has been persistent speculation that japans central bank 
will again raise its official discount rate by as much as 1 
percentage point from the current 425 percent 
the discount rate the interest rate charged on loans by the 
central bank to commercial banks affects other domestic interest 
rates higher interest rates tend to enhance yendenominated 
investments 
